---
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About Ugo Giordano"
>
	<p>
		I'm Ugo Giordano, a Senior Software Engineer at Red Hat on the OpenShift AI
		platform team. I contribute to the Kubernetes operators that power the platform
		and focus on hardening its security posture. I work across 20+ repositories,
		building Go libraries, admission webhooks, and CI/CD automation. I'm particularly
		interested in how AI integrates into real developer tooling, not as a chatbot
		but as an agent that can actually do things.
	</p>

	<h2 class="text-text-muted font-normal mt-12 mb-5 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">What I'm working on</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Remediating a platform-wide RBAC misconfiguration across 22 operators</li>
		<li>Building a chaos engineering framework for Kubernetes operators (<a href="https://github.com/opendatahub-io/operator-chaos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">operator-chaos</a>)</li>
		<li>Automating security assessments across 135+ repositories using AI-powered analysis</li>
		<li>Contributing upstream fixes to controller-runtime operator patterns (<a href="/blog/protect-operator-from-oomkill/">OOMKill vulnerability</a>)</li>
	</ul>

	<h2 class="text-text-muted font-normal mt-12 mb-5 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Background</h2>
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
		<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
			<span class="text-text-muted text-xs whitespace-nowrap mt-1" style="font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;">2024–now</span>
			<div>
				<strong>Senior Software Engineer</strong> · Red Hat, OpenShift AI Platform
				<p class="text-sm mt-1">Security hardening, operator development, DevSecOps automation.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
			<span class="text-text-muted text-xs whitespace-nowrap mt-1" style="font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;">2021–2024</span>
			<div>
				<strong>Software Maintenance Engineer</strong> · Red Hat
				<p class="text-sm mt-1">Production escalations for enterprise OpenShift clients in financial services and telecom.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
			<span class="text-text-muted text-xs whitespace-nowrap mt-1" style="font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;">2017–2021</span>
			<div>
				<strong>Project Manager & Senior Software Engineer</strong> · RisLab
				<p class="text-sm mt-1">Cyber-physical protection systems correlating PSIM and SIEM events for critical infrastructure.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
			<span class="text-text-muted text-xs whitespace-nowrap mt-1" style="font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;">2016–2017</span>
			<div>
				<strong>Ph.D. Intern, Member of Technical Staff</strong> · Nokia Bell Labs, New Jersey
				<p class="text-sm mt-1">Cloud benchmarking frameworks for NetUNIX, a carrier-grade network operating system.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2 class="text-text-muted font-normal mt-12 mb-5 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Education</h2>
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
		<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
			<span class="text-text-muted text-xs whitespace-nowrap mt-1" style="font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;">2014–2019</span>
			<div>
